{"title":"czq的大陆划分","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期","搜索","图论","并查集"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1230#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1230","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1230/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1230/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1230"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一张eu4地图由$n$个省份构成，某些省份之间会有陆路相连，一组极大的由陆路互相联通的省份构成的集合称为大陆。\r\n\r\n每个省份都有发展度$a_i$，大陆的发展度为其省份发展度之和。czq想知道，所有大陆中发展度最大的为多少，最小的为多少？"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个整数$n,m$，指省份的个数和陆路连接的个数。\r\n\r\n接下来一行$n$个整数$a_i$，为每个省份的发展度。\r\n\r\n接下来$m$行，每行两个整数$u_i,v_i$，指这两个省份之间有陆路相连。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅一行两个整数，由空格隔开，为大陆最大的发展度和最小的发展度。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n7 5\r\n1 9 2 6 8 1 7\r\n1 3\r\n3 6\r\n6 1\r\n4 5\r\n7 2\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n16 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例解释\r\n```\r\n共有三个大陆：{1，3，6}——发展度为4，{2,7}——发展度为16，{4,5}——发展度为14\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq m \\leq 2 \\times 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq a_i \\leq 100$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq u_i,v_i \\leq n$"}]}